drm/tinydrm: add support for LEGO MINDSTORMS EV3 LCD

LEGO MINDSTORMS EV3 has an LCD with a ST7586 controller. This adds a new
module for the ST7586 controller with parameters for the LEGO MINDSTORMS
EV3 LCD display.

